<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<title>Threshold Activated - iGreenMon</title>
	</head>

	<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; padding: 2rem; color: #333">
		<h2>Threshold Activated</h2>
		<p>Hi <%= user %>,</p>
		<p>
			One of your thresholds in greenhouse 
			<strong><%= greenhouse %></strong> has been activated.
		</p>
		<p>
			<strong><%= threshold %></strong> was triggered because the following 
			condition(s) were reached:
		</p>
		<ul style="color: #555">
			<% conditions.forEach((condition) => { %>
				<li><%= condition.output %> <%= condition.type %> <%= condition.value %></li>
			<% }) %>
		</ul>
		<p style="margin: 2rem 0; color: #555">
			Please sign in to your iGreenMon account for more details and to manage this threshold.
		</p>
		<p style="margin-top: 2rem">
			Stay safe,<br />
			The iGreenMon Team
		</p>
	</body>
</html>
